We can use this to write sever side code. Although you are not limited to the server
Focuses on internal system to use JS

Uses:
Create server & listen for incoming request

handle request, validate input, connect to DB

Return responses(Render HTML, JSON)

CORE MODULES WITH NODE
http -launch server, send request
https - launch a SSL server 
fs - 
path 
os 

createServer - takes a request listener, will execute for every incoming request 

node <nameoffile.js> 
